snippet.title: Dream Daddy: Dadrector's Cut - Trailer
snippet.description:
Dream Daddy: Dadrector's Cut | Available October 30th

Welcome back to Maple Bay! Dream Daddy: Dadrector's cut features cut content, new sidequests, and a brand new minigame! Available October 30th for PS4 and PC/Mac. Free update for those who already own the game!
